label: A2B8C11_tI84_139_h_deim_eh2n-001
title: Sc$_{11}$Al$_{2}$Ge$_{8}$ Structure
comments:
This is a tenary form of \href{current_web_home_dir/A10B11_tI84_139_dehim_eh2n-001}{Ho$_{11}$Ge$_{10}$}. The ICSD lists all these compounds using the Ho$_{11}$Ge$_{10}$ prototype. We arbitrarily chose Sc$_{11}$Al$_{2}$Ge$_{8}$ as the prototype. 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/A6B4C11_tI84_139_hm_dei_eh2n-001}{Tb$_{11}$Si$_{4}$In$_{6}$} is a second ternary form of Ho$_{11}$Ge$_{10}$. 
 The AFLOW standard labeling algorithm shifts the origin by (0.5 a, 0.5 b, 0), moving the Ge III atom from the published (8j) Wyckoff position to (8i).
